This challenge consists of 5 parts. For every part you can obtain one or more letters, depending on the difficulty of that part. Sometimes you will be asked to answer a HintMachineQuestion. Please provide your answer (your key) to that question to the Hint Machine applet below. When you have all letters, you can obtain the solution for this challenge.<br><p>
Luckily you can use my Hint Machine applet again. I changed it a bit and now your key is not restricted to just numbers. You can also put a word as a key :-)<br>
Please do not brute force the applet for valid keys, because you won't get something useful from it...

